        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-05-03 08:24:14.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe test machine of Jenkins uses an older version of Docker (1.12) so it seems unhappy with the old syntax of `docker inspect`, NBI_IP will then be set to the full output of the `docker inspect` command instead of the container ip address. However no error has been raised because the for-loop at the end of the script forces the machine to wait *465 seconds* in total before launching the robot tests, more than enough for the nbi container to be ready for connections. This patch will fix that error and reduce the test duration.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
